# рџЋ“ Student Pass Prediction using AWS SageMaker

## рџ“Њ Project Overview

This project builds and deploys a Machine Learning model using **Logistic Regression** to predict whether a student will pass based on the number of study hours.

The model is deployed using **AWS SageMaker**, enabling real-time predictions via an endpoint.

