---

## вљ пёЏ Important Notes

### рџ”ё 1. Endpoint Cost

SageMaker endpoints run continuously.

рџ‘‰ Stop after use:

```
predictor.delete_endpoint()
```

---

### рџ”ё 2. Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue                        | Fix                                       |
| ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Endpoint stuck in "Creating" | Use `ml.m5.large` instance                |
| `train.py not found`         | Ensure correct working directory          |
| 500 Internal Server Error    | Add `input_fn`, `predict_fn`, `output_fn` |
| Prediction fails             | Use correct serializer (`CSVSerializer`)  |

